<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Upma Recipe</title>
	<link href="~/css/upma.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

   
    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>🥣 Upma</h1>
        

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>1 cup Rava (Semolina/Sooji)</li>
            <li>2 cups Water</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Oil or Ghee</li>
            <li>1 tsp Mustard Seeds</li>
            <li>1 tsp Urad Dal</li>
            <li>1 tsp Chana Dal</li>
            <li>1 Green Chili (Chopped)</li>
            <li>1-inch Ginger (Grated)</li>
            <li>1 Small Onion (Chopped)</li>
            <li>1 Carrot (Chopped)</li>
            <li>1/4 cup Green Peas</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Coriander Leaves</li>
            <li>1 tsp Lemon Juice</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <h3>Step 1: Roast the Rava</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Dry roast the rava in a pan on low heat until aromatic. Set aside.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 2: Prepare the Tempering</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Heat oil in a pan and add mustard seeds.</li>
            <li>Once they splutter, add urad dal, chana dal, green chilies, and ginger.</li>
            <li>Sauté for a minute, then add onions and cook until translucent.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 3: Cook the Vegetables</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Add chopped carrots and green peas. Cook for 2 minutes.</li>
            <li>Pour in 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 4: Add Rava</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Slowly add the roasted rava while stirring continuously.</li>
            <li>Cook on low heat until the water is absorbed and upma becomes fluffy.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 5: Finish & Serve</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Add coriander leaves and a squeeze of lemon juice.</li>
            <li>Mix well and serve hot with coconut chutney.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
